        <li>Customize the content you see when you use the Services – for example, location information is used to tag the location of a story reported by a user, which location may be edited by the user;</li>
        <li>For any other purposes disclosed to you at the time we collect your information or pursuant to your consent.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h3>3. Disclosure of information</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>We are committed to maintaining your trust, and we want you to understand when and with whom we may share the information we collect.</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>General Public. We may disclose information to the general public if you submit content in a public forum, such as stories or comments on such stories.</li>
        <li>Research. We may disclose your anonymized information to third party researchers for research purposes. All data will be based on anonymously classified and logged data (age, gender, etc.) which is not related with the personalized profile or preference of the user.</li>
        <li>With your consent. We may share information for any other purposes disclosed to you at the time we collect the information or pursuant to your consent.</li>
      </ul>
